high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the fork on the counter.
Step to the right to face the stove.
Place the fork in the pan on the back right burner.
Pick up the pan on the back right burner.
Turn left and step forward to face the counter.
Place the pan with the fork in it on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To put a fork in a pan plus move it to the left side counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the stove.
Take the fork from the counter to the left of the stove.
Move to the right side of the stove.
Put the fork in the frying pan.
Pick up the frying pan from the stove.
Turn left and walk to the counter.
Place the frying pan on the counter to the left of the ladle with the blue handle.
anns.task_desc: Place a frying pan with a fork inside on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward, turn right, go forward to the counter to the left of the oven.
Take the fork from the counter.
Go to the right to the oven, face the oven.
Put the fork in the right pan on the stove top.
Take the pan from the stove top.
Turn left, go forward to the counter.
Put the pan to the left of the large spoon on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a fork in it on a counter.
